<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
<title>Khen Lohna Vangkhaw Lun</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gal in dawn leng thangvan khawpi,
 Khen lohna gam ngo bang a lang;
 Gibang khenni a hung tun in,
 Khen lohna gam ka ngai.

[V2]
 A chawm ngei ie lei nunnawpna,
 Pak bangin a tuoi kit tai;
 Kikhen lo thei I hi puou maw,
 Lenna mun a dan ziekin ?

[V3]
 2. Mu bang ka ngai khen lohna gam,
 Nun nuom sawl bang I hei na ding;
 Bang tik leh thuongte I tung dem?
 Khenlohna vangkhuo lun.

[V4]
 3. Gimtheih thuoka I kikhen hin,
 Bangtik tui bang I kigawm dem?
 Nuoi simlei thuong nung I sieh tieng
 Luon tui bang kigawm ding

[V5]
 4. Khen lohna vang khawpi ka ngai,
 Simlei a gi bang kikhen ni'n;
 Lungkham sawlang ban na'ng um lo,
 Simlei gimum ahin.

[V6]
 5. I kikhen a I kah lai hin,
 Thangvan gam nuom galin dawn leng;
 Kikhen a um loh ka het in,
 Tunkal ngakla'n ka kap.</lyrics>
</song>